r />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;exclusion&gt; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;groupId&gt;org.springframework.boot&lt;/groupId&gt; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;artifactId&gt;spring-boot-starter-tomcat&lt;/artifactId&gt; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/exclusion&gt; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/exclusions&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/dependency&gt;</p>\n\n<p>3）然后修改&lt;build&gt;&lt;/build&gt;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;build&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;resources&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;resource&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;directory&gt;src/main/java&lt;/directory&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;includes&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;include&gt;**/*.xml&lt;/include&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/includes&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/resource&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;resource&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;directory&gt;src/main/resources&lt;/directory&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;includes&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;include&gt;**.*&lt;/include&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;include&gt;**/*.*&lt;/include&gt;&lt;!-- i18n能读取到 --&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;include&gt;**/*/*.*&lt;/include&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/includes&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/resource&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/resources&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;plugins&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;plugin&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;groupId&gt;org.apache.maven.plugins&lt;/groupId&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;artifactId&gt;maven-war-plugin&lt;/artifactId&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;configuration&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;warName&gt;mogu_sms&lt;/warName&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;failOnMissingWebXml&gt;false&lt;/failOnMissingWebXml&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;outputDirectory&gt;webapps&lt;/outputDirectory&gt;<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&lt;/configuration&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/plugin&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/plugins&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;finalName&gt;mogu_sms&lt;/finalName&gt;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &lt;/build&gt;</p>\n\n<p>3) 然后在修改 Application.java 启动类，若打包成war包,则需要继承&nbsp;<strong>org.springframework.boot.context.web.SpringBootServletInitializer</strong>类,覆盖其config(SpringApplicationBuilder)方法</p>\n\n<p>@SpringBootApplication<br />\npublic class APP extends SpringBootServletInitializer{<br />\n&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; @Override<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; protected SpringApplicationBuilder configure(SpringApplicationBuilder builder) {<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; return builder.sources(APP.class);<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; }</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; public static void main(String[] args){<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; SpringApplication.run(APP.class,args);<br />\n&nbsp; &nbsp; }<br />\n}</p>\n\n<p>4）完成后，使用maven clean install 命令，就能看到在 项目根目录的webapps目录下，看到 打包好的war包了。<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>最后将全部模块弄好后，丢到阿里云的tomcat容器里面，部署了6个项目，大概占用60%内存，还不错~<img alt=\"\" src=\"http://120.79.70.126:8600/ckEditorUploadImg/1541210475637.png\" style=\"height:153px; width:582px\" /></p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n, 参数6:53c5a0f3142e4f54820315936f78383b, 参数7:2c93dfab0e754006866f8ed486923a41, 参数8:0, 参数9:1, 参数10:0, 参数11:1, 参数12:陌溪_, 参数13:蘑菇博客, 参数14:2508670a57b54a5b8f66dd7547d52cd1, ','编辑博客',1,'2018-12-04 10:58:55','2018-12-04 10:58:55'),('f338d8f342084648a77c14ab44817133','admin','192.168.154.1','/admin/restPwd','POST','com.moxi.mogublog.admin.restapi.AdminRestApi','restPwd','参数1:SecurityContextHolderAwareRequestWrapper[ FirewalledRequest[ org.apache.catalina.connector.RequestFacade@4e7f4b01]], 参数2:1f01cd1d2f474743b241d74008b12335, ','重置用户密码',1,'2018-11-22 18:36:23','2018-11-22 18:36:22'),('f3ffc6acf4da4a17ab40baff68b7ddb9','admin','192.168.154.1','/blogSort/edit','POST','com.moxi.mogublog.admin.restapi.BlogSortRestApi','edit','参数1:SecurityContextHolderAwareRequestWrapper[ FirewalledRequest[ org.apache.catalina.connector.RequestFacade@3ce1e9f2]], 参数2:093d8bdd01c84890a928e923d5c235fe, 参数3:时光轴, 参数4:时光飞逝，机会就在我们眼前，何时找到了灵感，就要把握机遇，我们需要智慧和勇气去把握机会, ','编辑博客分类',1,'2018-11-30 20:12:11','2018-11-30 20:12:11'),('fc6ad8d1d97d4722ac0a58baa8ca1f31','admin','192.168.31.230','/adminRole/edit','POST','com.moxi.mogublog.admin.restapi.AdminRoleRestApi','edit','参数1:SecurityContextHolderAwareRequestWrapper[ FirewalledRequest[ org.apache.catalina.connector.RequestFacade@d09810f]], 参数2:com.moxi.mogublog.xo.entity.AdminRole@43d79ea0, ','编辑权限',1,'2018-12-05 20:26:29','2018-12-05 20:26:29'),('fd156fee1ae040cca4e942e66350f231','admin','192.168.154.1','/admin/getList','GET','com.moxi.mogublog.admin.restapi.AdminRe